com.tailf.conf

Class SnmpVarbind

  • Object
    • com.tailf.conf.SnmpVarbind

  • public class SnmpVarbind
extends Object
    The SnmpVarbind is a data structure for holding an SNMP variable binding which is on either of the forms:
    • Variable - Value
    • OID - Value
    • Column - RowIndex - Value
